array_files[18]=new Array(0,1,"./documentation/Reference/T2D%20Class%20Reference/Video.html","2011-12-16","6K","Video    ","",""," Video Video Description: Video control functions. Methods: getDesktopResolution() Description: Get the width, height, and bitdepth of the screen. getDisplayDeviceList() getRes() Description: Get the width, height, and bitdepth of the screen. getResolutionList() getVideoDriverInfo() isDeviceFullScreenOnly(string deviceName) isFullScreen() Description: Is the game running full-screen? minimizeWindow() Description: Minimize the game window nextResolution() Description: Switch to next resolution. prevResolution() Description: Switch to previous resolution. restoreWindow() Description: Restore the game window setDisplayDevice(string deviceName, int width, int height=NULL, int bpp=NULL, bool fullScreen=NULL) Description: Attempt to set the screen mode using as much information as is provided. setRes(int width, int height, int bpp=NULL) setScreenMode(int width, int height, int bpp, bool fullScreen) setVerticalSync(bool f) switchBitDepth() Description: Switch between 16 or 32 bits. Only works in full screen. toggleFullScreen() videoSetGammaCorrection() Description: setGammaCorrection(gamma); Home Back to Top     ");
